msgid "Offer Services"
msgstr "Pakkuge teenuseid"

#: inc/lib/ai-builder/inc/assets/build/main.js:191
msgid "For service-based businesses. Helps create service pages and booking functionality."
msgstr "Teenusepõhiste ettevõtete jaoks. Aitab luua teenuse lehti ja broneerimisfunktsionaalsust."

